posts.post_title: WTB T206 Nelson Tisdel Back Stamps
posts.post_content:
I’ve collected several Tisdel back stamps from members here, and would love to add some more.  Great backstory to that stamp.  

I own seven Tisdel stamps currently, and looking to see how many more of those cards I can re-assemble!
bumping this up, to see if anyone has some.  Willing to trade other back stamps for Tisdel's as well.  thanks

I picked up my 8th Tisdel stamp over the weekend on ebay!  Would love continue trying to re-assemble the collection.  

Bumping this up to see if there is anyone who has a T206 stamped Tisdel they would be willing to sell.  Also willing to trade a different stamped card in my collection for any Tisdel.  Thanks

Added two more Tisdels in the past couple weeks, thanks to a pair of great board members!  Up to 10 total.  

Still looking to buy others if they are out there.  I’m also willing to trade for them, in your favor value wise.
